headline: Why MGM Resorts (MGM) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of hospitality and casino entertainment company MGM Resorts (NYSE:MGM) jumped 2.6% in the morning session after its proposal to obtain a full downstate casino license in New York received a key preliminary approval.
